      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how none of this actually matters. like, we're just biological accidents on a rock that's eventually going to be swallowed by the sun, and then even the stars will go out. everything we do, every feeling, every struggle... it's just noise before an eternal silence. does it even make sense to keep trying when the end result is just zero?",
